# Markdown docs are kept local-only — the public repo ships just the README.
# (ARCHITECTURE, PORTAGE, CHANGELOG, INPUT, LIGHT, TIMECODE, RELEASING, PROGRESS,
#  WHATSNEXT, RENAME, CLAUDE… all stay on your machine. vendor/asiosdk/README.md
#  is already tracked and stays.)
*.md
!README.md

